/target
/tools/component-interface-snapshot/target/
/tools/rust-facade-snapshot/target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.orig
.DS_Store
*.xcuserstate
xcuserdata/
/ios/**/build/
/android/**/build/
.gradle/
*.swp

# M4 packaging outputs (scripts/build-swift-xcframework.sh) -- regenerated
# from source, never committed: /gen holds the raw uniffi-bindgen dump, and
# Packages/NMP/NMP.xcframework + Packages/NMP/Sources/NMPFFI/nmp_ffi.swift
# are its split (headers-only vs Swift-source) outputs. Package.swift +
# Sources/NMP/ (the hand-written ergonomic layer) ARE committed -- only the
# generated/compiled pieces are ignored here. A clean clone must run the
# build script once before `swift build`/`swift test` work; see
# Packages/NMP/README.md (#18) and the `swift-package` CI job, which proves
# this exact path from a fresh checkout on every push.
/gen
/Packages/NMP/NMP.xcframework
/Packages/NMP/Sources/NMPFFI

# SwiftPM's own build cache (`swift build`/`swift test` output) -- always
# regenerated, never committed, same as /target above.
/Packages/NMP/.build
/Packages/NMP/.swiftpm

# M5 falsifier app -- xcodegen-generated project (memory:
# xcodegen-pbxproj-churn -- xcodegen churns pbxproj UUIDs on every regen, so
# the .xcodeproj itself is never committed; only `project.yml` + `Sources/`
# are the source of truth). Regenerate via `xcodegen generate` in
# apps/Falsifier.
/apps/Falsifier/Falsifier.xcodeproj
/apps/Falsifier/Generated-Info.plist
/apps/Falsifier/build/
/apps/Falsifier/DerivedData/

# NMP UI Gallery -- same xcodegen/build-output discipline as Falsifier.
/apps/UIGallery/NMPUIGallery.xcodeproj
/apps/UIGallery/Generated-Info.plist
/apps/UIGallery/build/
/apps/UIGallery/DerivedData/
/apps/UIGallery/.derivedData/

# #40 Kotlin/Flow falsifier packaging outputs
# (scripts/build-kotlin-jvm.sh) -- same discipline as the Swift block above:
# /gen-kotlin holds the raw uniffi-bindgen dump, and
# Packages/NMPKotlin/src/main/kotlin/uniffi + src/main/resources are its
# split (Kotlin-source vs native-lib) outputs. build.gradle.kts/
# settings.gradle.kts + src/main/kotlin/com/nmp/sdk (the hand-written
# ergonomic layer) + src/test ARE committed -- only the generated/compiled
# pieces are ignored here. A clean clone must run the build script once
# before `./gradlew test` works; see Packages/NMPKotlin/README.md and the
# `kotlin-package` CI job.
/gen-kotlin
/Packages/NMPKotlin/src/main/kotlin/uniffi
/Packages/NMPKotlin/src/main/resources
/Packages/NMPKotlin/build/
/Packages/NMPKotlin/.gradle/
tmp
